WEBVTT

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.576
Salom,
burger to’ldirib berasizmi?

00:07:30.600 --> 00:07:32.776
(Kulgu)

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:35.256
U chalkashib ketdi.
“Burger to’ldirish nima degani?”

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:36.536
(Kulgu)

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:40.216
Shunday dedim “Xo’sh, bu xuddi ichimlik
to’ldirib berishga o’xshaydi, lekin

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:42.736
o’rniga burger”
U: “Uzr, bizda burger to’ldirishning

00:07:42.760 --> 00:07:44.096
imkoni yo’q” dedi.
(Kulgu)

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:48.176
Ana shunda rad javobini oldim. Ketib
qolsam bo’lardi, biroq bunday qilmadim.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.336
Shunday dedim, “Burgerlaring menga yoqadi,

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.776
oshxonangiz ham chakkimas,

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.896
burger to’ldirish imkoniyatini
berganlaringda

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.256
sizlarni yanada
yaxshi

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:56.536
ko'rardim.
(Kulgu)

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:59.176
U esa “Mayli, menejerimga buni 
aytaman, ehtimol

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:02.176
bunday imkoniyat berilar,
ammo bugun qila olmaymiz” dedi.